# Finding Similar Movies
We'll start by loading up the MovieLens dataset, Using Pandas, we can very quickly load the rows of the u.data and u.item files that we care about, and merge them togheter so we can work with movie names instead of ID's. (in a real production job, you'd stick with ID's and worry about the names at the display layer to make things more efficient. But this lets us understadn what's going on better for now.)
